        "Dharmesh D Bhuva",
        "Ning Liu"
      ],
      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gkad1026"
      },
      "sc:description": "standR is an user-friendly R package providing functions to assist conducting good-practice analysis of Nanostring's GeoMX DSP data. All functions in the package are built based on the SpatialExperiment object, allowing integration into various spatial transcriptomics-related packages from Bioconductor. standR allows data inspection, quality control, normalization, batch correction and evaluation with informative visualizations.",
